# 3) Final Documentation / Quickstart (Step-by-step, copy-ready)

## A. Prerequisites
- Python 3.8+  
- GPU (NVIDIA + CUDA recommended) for training  
- pip, git installed

## B. Install (local)
```bash
git clone <your-repo-url>
cd yolov8_detection_project
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate       # Windows: venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
